eed the money.\n\n- Wilhelm\n|\nWhen life throws you a curve ball just give up, no need messing around with that off speed shit\n\n- Bradley\n|\nSometimes you have to choose between being strong and being honest, if you want real answers.\n\n- Jessiqua Wittman, A Memoir of Mercy\n|\nYou are important to this earth. If you were meant to journey alone, you would not have friends...\n\n- Virginia\n|\nEmbrace faith, hope and love.\n\n- Lailah Gifty Akita, Think Great: Be Great!"